data.description:
Wood-look vinyl plank flooring throughout. Living room with ceiling fan. Living/dining combination. Fully equipped kitchen with pantry. Family room on back of house with access to backyard. Master bedroom with ceiling an & walk-in closet. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. Inside laundry with washer & dryer - "as is" - no warranty. Open patio. No smokers. Small pets considered with owner approval. 

Increased security deposit may be required for roommates.

Elementary School: Brentwood
Middle School: Workman
High School: Pensacola High
